# Add Product Differentiator

Review the built landing page, then design and implement a custom interactive widget that is unique to this product — something competitors do not have. This is the "plus" element that makes visitors remember the page.

<EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>
This is NOT a standard section. Do NOT build a generic feature grid, FAQ accordion, or pricing table. Build something custom, interactive, and memorable that showcases the product's unique value.
</EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>

## Process

```dot
digraph differentiator {
    rankdir=TB;
    read [label="Read built LP source\nand context files" shape=box];
